Package com.commander4j.c4jWS

Class JDBControl

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.c4jWS.JDBControl
public class JDBControl extends Object
JDBControl class is used to insert/update/delete the SYS_CONTROL table. This table is used to hold configuration information for the application.
